hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: The line's engaged duleekpharmacy.com Since when did looking like a walking highlighter become cool? Whenever I see a team debut that ugly accent color on their uniforms, it screams of desperation. Are they hoping to attract crows? Crows like shiny things. Maybe some marketing guy at Nike forgot the “d” in “crowds” and issued a memo saying teams were worried about not drawing big crows at their games. That’s the only explanation that seems reasonable.
